PEOPLE
v.
GARCIA S230616 Supreme Court of California August 17, 2016

*271Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division Two, with directions to vacate its decision and reconsider the cause in light of People v. Franklin (2016) 63 Cal.4th 261, 268-269, 283-284, 202 Cal.Rptr.3d 496, 370 P.3d 1053. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
